Package: promises
Type: Package
Title: A tidy API for lazy and non-standard evaluation.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2017-01-23
Author: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Peter Meilstrup <peter.meilstrup@gmail.com>
Description: A library for working with lazy and non-standard evalution in R, covering inspection of unevaluated arguments, manipulation of ... argument lists, and creation of calls.
